    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but you just said earlier that debt reduction is \"essential\" and \"must be the immediate focus.\" now you're calling it \"short-sighted\" to ignore social programs. so which is it? is it the responsible path or is it a gamble? it feels like you're just flip-flopping to try and sound middle-of-the-road.",
